// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1558 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 27d72dcf-32ff-5f9a-b12b-d43e5e0c226b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*")
